# MCPAgentAI üöÄ 

[![PyPI](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/mcpagentai.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/mcpagentai/)
[![Python Versions](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/mcpagentai.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/mcpagentai/)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/pypi/l/mcpagentai.svg)](https://github.com/mcpagents-ai/mcpagentai/blob/main/LICENSE)

**MCPAgentAI** is a standardized **tool wrapping framework** for implementing and managing diverse tools in a unified way. It is designed to help developers quickly integrate and launch tool-based use cases.

### Key Features
- üîß **Standardized Wrapping**: Provides an abstraction layer for building tools using the MCP protocol.
- üöÄ **Flexible Use Cases**: Easily add or remove tools to fit your specific requirements.
- ‚ú® **Out-of-the-Box Tools**: Includes pre-built tools for common scenarios:
  - üê¶ **Twitter Management**: Automate tweeting, replying, and managing Twitter interactions.
  - üí∏ Crypto: Get the latest cryptocurrency prices.
  - ü§ñ [ElizaOS](https://github.com/elizaos/eliza) Integration: Seamlessly connect and interact with ElizaOS for enhanced automation.
  - üïë Time utilities
  - ‚òÅÔ∏è Weather information (API)
  - üìö Dictionary lookups
  - üßÆ Calculator for mathematical expressions
  - üíµ Currency exchange (API)
  - üìà Stocks Data: Access real-time and historical stock market information.
  - [WIP] üì∞ News: Retrieve the latest news headlines.

### Tech Stack üõ†Ô∏è
- **Python**: Core programming language
- **[MCP](https://pypi.org/project/mcp/) Framework**: Communication protocol
- **Docker**: Containerization

#### ü§î What is MCP?

The **Model Context Protocol ([MCP](https://modelcontextprotocol.io/introduction))** is a cutting-edge standard for **context sharing and management** across AI models and systems. Think of it as the **language** AI agents use to interact seamlessly. üß†‚ú®

Here‚Äôs why **MCP** matters:

- üß© **Standardization**: MCP defines how context can be shared across models, enabling **interoperability**.
- ‚ö° **Scalability**: It‚Äôs built to handle large-scale AI systems with high throughput.
- üîí **Security**: Robust authentication and fine-grained access control.
- üåê **Flexibility**: Works across diverse systems and AI architectures.

![mcp_architecture](https://imageio.forbes.com/specials-images/imageserve/674aaa6ac3007d55b62fc2bf/MCP-Architecture/960x0.png?height=559&width=711&fit=bounds)
[source](https://www.forbes.com/sites/janakirammsv/2024/11/30/why-anthropics-model-context-protocol-is-a-big-step-in-the-evolution-of-ai-agents/)
