## Development üõ†Ô∏è

1. **Clone this repository:**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/mcpagents-ai/mcpagentai.git
   cd mcpagentai
   ```

2. **(Optional) Create a virtual environment:**
   ```bash
   python3 -m venv .venv
   source .venv/bin/activate
   ```

3. **Install dependencies:**
   ```bash
   pip install -e .
   ```

4. **Build the package:**
   ```bash
   python -m build
   ```
